HEADWORD: Papain
<hw>Pa*pa"in</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Papaw</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Physiol. Chem.)</fld> <def>A proteolytic
